---
// "Got your own project in mind?" pinned sidebar card. Designed to sit at
// position:sticky inside a 2-column layout, channelling Deuce's journal
// sidebar pattern but keeping the Rooftop palette.
---

<aside class="md:sticky md:top-28 self-start">
  <div
    class="p-6 md:p-7"
    style="background-color:var(--color-mint);color:var(--color-navy-900);border-radius:var(--radius-card-md);"
  >
    <p
      style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.01em;"
    >
      Got your own project in mind?
    </p>
    <p
      class="mt-2"
      style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.95rem;color:rgba(13,32,48,0.78);line-height:1.5;"
    >
      Tell us what you're scaling, launching, or rebuilding, and we'll talk it through.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/contact/"
      class="inline-flex items-center mt-4 px-5 py-3"
      style="background-color:var(--color-navy-900);color:#ffffff;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);font-family:var(--font-sans);font-weight:600;font-size:0.95rem;"
    >
      Let's chat
    </a>
  </div>
</aside>
